import Mathlib

open Set

/-- If U ‚äÇ ‚ÑÇ is open and f : ‚ÑÇ ‚Üí ‚ÑÇ is holomorphic (differentiable on U) and injective on U,
then f'(z) ‚â† 0 for every z ‚àà U. -/
theorem injective_holomorphic_deriv_ne_zero (U : Set ‚ÑÇ) (f : ‚ÑÇ ‚Üí ‚ÑÇ)
  (hU : IsOpen U) (hd : DifferentiableOn ‚ÑÇ f U)
  (h_inj : ‚àÄ x y, x ‚àà U ‚Üí y ‚àà U ‚Üí f x = f y ‚Üí x = y) :
  ‚àÄ z ‚àà U, deriv f z ‚â† 0 := by sorry
